1463.name: SA Alloy 825 strip
1463.Applications: SA Alloy 825 is a nickel-iron-chromium-molybdenum-copper cladding alloy for use in extremely corrosive environments.
1463.Suitable_For: SA Alloy 825 is specially designed for cladding lower alloyed parts to obtain a high quality clad layer against corrosion. Designations: 825 (2.4858, UNS N08825). 1.4500, 1.4529, 1.4539, 2.4858, 1.4563, G-X7NiCrMoCuNb 25 20, X1NiCrMoCuN25 20 6, X1NiCrMoCuN25 20 5, NiCr21Mo, X1NiCrMoCu 31 27 4, N08926, N08904, ALLOY 825, N08028, UNS N08825
